content: STRADEUM is one of the largest single-family Live Houses in Asia. It integrates audition rooms, recording studios, display centers and coffee bars, designed by Mr. SAM TOYOSHIMA, a world-renowned studio designer.
It's leisurely, there are many brunch cafes, and even the park toilets are clean and well maintained :)
When I'm good, I'm in Central Park.
The street from Sunken Square is really pretty :)
The night view is pretty and it's a great place to go during the day
I love Puffy in Central Park.
